The  Information Technology Shared Services department provides IT support to A*STAR  and its Research Institutes through innovative and integrated exploitation of  Information Technology.
We  are looking for motivated staff for the CERT team within  the A*STAR ITSS Department. Key responsibilities include:

 Handle  security incidents end-to-end with root cause analysis and excellent  problem-solving skills.
 Conduct  security investigations, digital forensics, identify cyber threats, assess  impact and provide recommendations.
 Work with  GovTech as well as internal stakeholders, and respond promptly and effectively  to security alerts.
 Conduct and  follow up on VA/PT.
 Participate in  Red/Blue teaming and other exercises.
 Review  existing security controls and recommend appropriate solutions to address  gaps.
 Explore and  recommend new security technologies, solutions and  processes.

JOB  REQUIREMENTS

 Background  in IT management, infrastructure, cybersecurity, and/or security  management
 At  least 3 to 5 years of prior experience in relevant areas
 Strong  written and verbal communication skills
 Able  to work with multi-disciplinary teams to deliver results effectively and  efficiently